<p>it was transformation multiplication of sines in the left part of trigonometrical inequality</p>



<p>***</p>



<p>1.</p>



<math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block">
    <mfrac>
      <mrow>
        <msin>
